               <p>I am wife of 
               <persName id="t17760221-27-person306">
                  Peter
                   Smith
               <interp inst="t17760221-27-person306" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17760221-27-person306" type="given" value="Peter"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17760221-27-person306" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            : the prisoner is a <rs id="t17760221-27-deflabel142" type="occupation">locksmith</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17760221-27-defend302 t17760221-27-deflabel142"></join>, I employed him to do a job on Friday week; I saw the spoons on Friday, and missed them the next morning; the prisoner did not come to finish the job; he was taken on the Tuesday following, when he confessed he took the spoons and shovel.</p>
               <p>
            
