               <p>I am a pawnbroker: on the 13th of February the prisoner pledged this silver table spoon<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177602210027"></xptr> (producing it) with me in the name of 
               <persName id="t17760221-27-person308">
                  James
                   Pennington
